question: Which booking had the most passengers in the second quarter of 2024?
query:
SELECT p.booking_id,
       COUNT(DISTINCT p.passenger_id) AS passenger_count
FROM postgres_air.boarding_pass bp
JOIN postgres_air.passenger p ON bp.passenger_id = p.passenger_id
WHERE bp.boarding_time >= '2024-04-01' 
  AND bp.boarding_time < '2024-07-01'
GROUP BY p.booking_id
ORDER BY passenger_count DESC
LIMIT 1;
